import React from "react" import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom' import './Home.css' class Login extends React.Component { render() { return ( < div class = "loginForm" > < form > < input className = "login-input" type = "input" placeholder = "Email" name = "email" id = 'email' required / > < br > < /br>

< input className = "login-input" type = "input" placeholder = "Nickname" name = "nick" id = 'nick' required / > < br > < /br>

< input className = "login-input" type = "input" placeholder = "Game code" name = "code" id = 'code' required / > < br > < /br>

< button className = "button-27" > Join Game < /button> < /form> < /div> ) } } export default Login
